{"badges":["TM5","TM6"],"preparations":[{"content":["Place water in mixing bowl.","Insert simmering basket and weigh in beetroot pieces. Cook <b>30-40 min\/120°C\/speed 0.5<b> until tender. Remove simmering basket with aid of spatula. Discard cooking water. Set beetroot aside to cool for 30 minutes.","After this time, place tahini, lemon juice, garlic, cooled cooked beetroot, ice and salt in mixing bowl then blend <b>30 sec\/speed 9<b>. Scrape down sides of mixing bowl with spatula then blend again <b>30 sec\/speed 9<b>.","Transfer to a serving bowl then drizzle with olive oil and sprinkle with pine nuts.","Serve with warm pitta bread."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"","content":["750 g water","450 g raw beetroots, peeled, quartered","225 g tahini","45 g lemon juice","2 garlic cloves","3 ice cubes","¼ tsp fine sea salt","extra virgin olive oil, for dizzling","1 Tbsp toasted pine nuts, for garnishing"]}],"id":"r342571","imageLink":"https:\/\/3.bp.blogspot.com\/-Rg3cI4j8DL8\/XZafEowEMXI\/AAAAAAAAgq8\/CHdSYJgLwvoi-vG26tAkIDTHL1SRew9DwCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_hADsvaWjP_v68o67.png","title":"Tahini and Beetroot Dip","publishedAt":"2018-06-14T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"8 g","fat":"17.6 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"5.6 g","calories":"910 kJ \/ 220 kcal"},"usefulItems":"serving bowl","hintsAndTricks":["Use the same weight of cooked beetroot and skip <b>steps 1<b> and 2."],"basicInfo":["easy","5m","1h 15m","8 portions"]}